Step 2: Implement Signature Verification
Complete the verify_signature() function with these requirements:

Generate HMAC-SHA256 hash of the payload using the secret key
Compare with the signature from the X-Hub-Signature-256 header
Use hmac.compare_digest() for secure comparison
Expected header format: sha256=<hexdigest>
Hints:

# Create HMAC object
expected_signature = hmac.new(
    key=WEBHOOK_SECRET.encode(),
    msg=payload_body,
    digestmod=hashlib.sha256
).hexdigest()

# Format for comparison
expected_sig = f"sha256={expected_signature}"
