Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Signature verification always fails

Ensure the secret key matches between server and client
Verify you're using raw request body (bytes) for signature calculation
Check header format is exactly sha256=<hexdigest>
Issue: Import errors

Confirm virtual environment is activated
Reinstall packages: pip install flask jsonschema
Issue: Port already in use

Change port in app.run() to 5001 or another available port
Kill existing process: sudo lsof -ti:5000 | xargs kill -9
Issue: Logs not writing

Check file permissions: ls -l webhook_events.log
Verify LOG_FILE path is correct
Ensure logging.basicConfig() is called before any logging
